          "terms_url": "https://www.geofabrik.de/en/data/download.html",
          "notes": "Downloads the AO's Geofabrik state/region extract. If osmium is installed on the Jetson, it clips to AOI; otherwise it registers the regional PBF and marks clipping as pending."
